==個人生活==
戴利於2010年8月23日創建了一個[[YouTube|YouTube]]頻道，他的頻道內容涵蓋多種主題，例如[[Vlog|Vlog]]、運動和食物，2021年8月，該頻道的訂閱人數突破100萬<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5ULOEYE9J0qQOZoKQ4BS6Q |title=Tom Daley |website=YouTube |language=en |access-date=31 July 2021 |archive-date=2021-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211030062036/https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5ULOEYE9J0qQOZoKQ4BS6Q |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年12月2日，他發佈了一部YouTube影片，說他今年的年初開始與一名男子交往，他說：「我從未如此快樂。（{{lang|en|I've never been happier.}}）」<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-devon-25183041 |title=Olympic diving star Tom Daley Daley reveals relationship with man |work=BBC News |date=2 December 2013 |access-date=2 December 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202124234/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-devon-25183041 |archive-date=2 December 2013 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite AV media |people=Daley, Tom (subject and author) |year=2013 |title=Tom Daley: Something I want to say... |medium=Home video |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OJwJnoB9EKw |access-date=2 December 2013 |publisher=Tom Daley |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202173848/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OJwJnoB9EKw |archive-date=2 December 2013 |url-status=live}}</ref>。戴利說公開談論他的私生活是一個艱難的決定，他說：「我以前從未體會到愛的感覺，它來得如此地快，我完全被愛淹沒了，以至於我總是無法將他從我腦海中抹去。（{{lang|en|I'd never felt the feeling of love, it happened so quickly, I was completely overwhelmed by it to the point I can't get him out of my head all the time.}}）」<ref>{{cite news |title=Olympic diver Tom Daley reveals it was 'love at first sight' when he met partner |url=http://www.itv.com/news/2013-12-05/olympic-diver-tom-daley-reveals-it-was-love-at-first-sight-when-he-met-partner/ |work=ITV News |date=5 December 2013 |access-date=14 December 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214021531/http://www.itv.com/news/2013-12-05/olympic-diver-tom-daley-reveals-it-was-love-at-first-sight-when-he-met-partner/ |archive-date=14 December 2013 |url-status=live}}</ref>，他的伴侶是曾獲奧斯卡獎的美國籍電影編劇、導演兼製片人[[達斯汀·蘭斯·布雷克|達斯汀·蘭斯·布雷克]] <ref>{{cite news |last1=Respers France |first1=Lisa |title=Tom Daley engaged to Dustin Lance Black |url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/02/entertainment/tom-daley-dustin-lance-black-engaged-feat/ |access-date=22 May 2016 |publisher=CNN |date=2 October 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625081140/http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/02/entertainment/tom-daley-dustin-lance-black-engaged-feat/ |archive-date=25 June 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>。

在影片中，他從未使用「[[男同性戀|男同性戀]]」或「[[雙性戀|雙性戀]]」等字詞，他說：「我當然仍然會喜歡女生。（{{lang|en|Of course I still fancy girls.}}）」。2015年7月，在[[衛報|衛報]]的採訪中，被問及有關性向的問題時，他說：「我不會將它貼上任何一種標籤，因為我現在與一位男性交往，但仍然會對女性產生性慾感覺。（{{lang|en|I don't put a particular label on any of it because right now I'm in a relationship with a guy, but I still have sexual feelings towards girls.}}）」<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/jul/18/tom-daley-i-always-knew-i-was-attracted-to-guys-olympic-2012-diver |title=Tom Daley: 'I always knew I was attracted to guys' |author=Simon Hattenstone |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=18 July 2015 |access-date=15 November 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151115001807/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/jul/18/tom-daley-i-always-knew-i-was-attracted-to-guys-olympic-2012-diver |archive-date=15 November 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>，當被問及他對自己同性傾向的接受與和布萊克的關係（{{lang|en|his coming to terms with his same-sex attraction and his relationship with Black.}}），他說：「我曾和女性交往，我會產生性慾感覺，但當我和蘭斯在一起時，這種感受變得更加強烈。（{{lang|en|I'd been in relationships with girls where I'd had sexual feelings, but it became so much more intense when I met Lance.}}）」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.towleroad.com/2015/07/tom-daley-bares-guardian-interview-dlb-olympics-growing-gay/ |title=Tom Daley Bares All In 'Guardian' Interview on Dating Dustin Lance Black, 2016 Olympics, and Growing Up Gay |last=Malec |first=Malec |work=[[towleroad|towleroad]] |date=18 July 2015 |access-date=8 December 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208235124/http://www.towleroad.com/2015/07/tom-daley-bares-guardian-interview-dlb-olympics-growing-gay/ |archive-date=8 December 2015 |url-status=live }}</ref>。2018年，在[[LGBT|LGBT]]媒體{{link-en|PinkNews|PinkNews}}的採訪中，他說他認為自己是[[酷兒|酷兒]]，並說：「我不是百分之百異性戀，也不是百分之百同性戀。（{{lang|en|I am not 100 percent straight; I am not 100 percent gay.}}）」<ref>{{cite web |last1=Jackman |first1=Josh |title=Tom Daley says he's queer, 'not 100 percent gay' |url=https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2018/04/24/tom-daley-says-hes-queer-not-100-percent-gay/ |website=PinkNews |access-date=8 February 2021 |archive-date=2022-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110014138/https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2018/04/24/tom-daley-says-hes-queer-not-100-percent-gay/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年7月，在[[2020年夏季奥林匹克运动会|東京奧運]]奪得金牌後的記者會當中，他稱自己為男同性戀者（{{lang|en|gay man}}）<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.lbc.co.uk/world-news/tom-daley-gets-first-olympic-gold-as-team-gb-wins-string-of-medals/ |title=Tokyo 2020: Team GB wins string of medals with Tom Daley getting first Olympic gold |author=Asher McShane |newspaper=[[LBC|LBC]] |date=26 July 2021 |access-date=26 July 2021 |url-status=no |archive-date=2022-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220101124138/https://www.lbc.co.uk/world-news/tom-daley-gets-first-olympic-gold-as-team-gb-wins-string-of-medals/ }}</ref>。

戴利和布萊克在一次的業界活動中相遇，戴利後來表示這是「真正的一見鍾情」<ref name="Horton"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/jul/30/tom-daley-if-i-hadnt-met-lance-i-dont-know-if-id-be-diving-now |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-07-31 |archive-date=2022-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220101231423/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/jul/30/tom-daley-if-i-hadnt-met-lance-i-dont-know-if-id-be-diving-now |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於2015年10月1日宣佈訂婚的喜訊<ref>{{cite news |author=Jenny Booth |url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/life/celebrity/article4573094.ece |title=Tom Daley gets engaged to his boyfriend |work=[[The_Times|The Times]] |date=1 October 2015 |access-date=1 October 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003022339/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/life/celebrity/article4573094.ece |archive-date=3 October 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/05/02/tom-daley-dustin-lance-black-relationship_n_5252128.html |title=Tom Daley Talks 'Crazy' Attention on His Relationship With Dustin Lance Black |work=[[HuffPost|HuffPost]] |date=2 May 2014 |access-date=4 May 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140504105053/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/05/02/tom-daley-dustin-lance-black-relationship_n_5252128.html |archive-date=4 May 2014 |url-status=live }}</ref>。2017年5月6日，戴利和布萊克在[[德文郡|德文郡]]的{{link-en|博維城堡|Bovey Castle}}舉行婚禮<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-devon-39836555 |title=Tom Daley and Dustin Lance Black marry at Devon hotel |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=6 May 2017 |access-date=7 May 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180501233808/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-devon-39836555 |archive-date=1 May 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>。2018年2月14日，戴利在Instagram上宣佈他與丈夫將有一個透過[[代孕|代孕]]而得的孩子<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-devon-43062264 |title=Tom Daley announces baby news |date=14 February 2018 |work=BBC News |access-date=14 February 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214164816/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-devon-43062264 |archive-date=14 February 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Horton">{{Cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/02/14/tom-daley-announces-partner-having-baby/ |title=Tom Daley announces he and his partner are having a baby |last=Horton |first=Helena |date=14 February 2018 |work=The Telegraph |access-date=14 February 2018 |issn=0307-1235 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214145218/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/02/14/tom-daley-announces-partner-having-baby/ |archive-date=14 February 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.sky.com/story/tom-daley-and-husband-are-having-a-baby-11250324 |title=Tom Daley and husband are having a baby |work=Sky News |access-date=14 February 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214171650/https://news.sky.com/story/tom-daley-and-husband-are-having-a-baby-11250324 |archive-date=14 February 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref>。2018年6月27日，他們的兒子羅伯特·「羅比」·雷·布雷克-戴利（{{lang|en|Robert "Robbie" Ray Black-Daley}}）出生<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/tom-daley-and-husband-have-baby-son-by-surrogate-f5vc3xskw |title=Tom Daley and husband have baby son by surrogate |first=Katie |last=Gibbons |date=30 June 2018 |newspaper=The Times |access-date=30 June 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630012144/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/tom-daley-and-husband-have-baby-son-by-surrogate-f5vc3xskw |archive-date=30 June 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref>。

